      "author": "hariiy-sys",
      "description": "### Fixes\r\n\r\n- **Wikipedia articles** now convert correctly to markdown:\r\n        \r\n    - Fixed broken references (no longer treated as wikilinks)\r\n        \r\n    - Fixed relative links (properly converted instead of `app://` format)\r\n        \r\n    - Fixed whitespace issues in text\r\n        \r\n        \r\n\r\n### Changes\r\n\r\n- Switched from **readability** to **defuddle** for content parsing\r\n    \r\n- Removed unused `excerpt` property (not supported by defuddle)\r\n  \r\n    \r\n\r\n### Thanks\r\n\r\nHuge thanks to **@unhighghlow** for contributing this fix!",
