      "author": "hariiy-sys",
      "description": "### What's New in 1.3.8\r\n\r\n####  Home Tab Customization\r\n- Set **custom background images** for your Home Tab\r\n- Adjust **blur intensity** for the background\r\n- Enjoy a refined **glassmorphism UI effect** for a sleek and modern look\r\n    \r\n\r\n####  Clipper View Card Customization\r\n\r\n- Gain full control over card appearance with toggles for:\r\n    - Article descriptions\r\n    - Author info\r\n    - Publication date\r\n    - Source domain\r\n    - Thumbnail images\r\n\r\n####  AI Prompt Management\r\n\r\n- **Export/import** your AI prompts as JSON\r\n- Enable or disable individual prompts on the fly\r\n    \r\n#### Enhanced AI Processing\r\n- **Preserve original content** when applying AI prompts\r\n- Toggle between **replace** and **preserve** modes\r\n- Your setting is **saved between sessions** for convenience",
